p:
“na cedaṃ snānamadṛṣṭārtham” ityādibhāṣyaṃ smṛtyarthavyākhyānaparam;
tasyārthamāha—yastvevamiti । yastu virodhaparihārāya āplavanaṃ smṛtyarthaṃ brūyāt
anyaṃ vā kathañcidadṛṣṭārthasaṃskāram, tasyottaram—“na cedam” iti bhāṣyeṇa ।।

LG.p:
“taccetpratyayitāt” ityasya yat pratyudāharaṇam “athāpratyayitāt” iti
tat “indriyaviṣayaṃ vā” ityasyāpratyayitavākyaprāmāṇyodāharaṇasya bādhakam;
“indriyaviṣayaṃ vā” ityasya ca yat pratyudāharaṇam “anindriyaviṣayaṃ vā” iti
tadapi “taccetpratyayitāt” ityasya śroturanindriyaviṣayodāharaṇasya bādhakam;

doṣavarjitaiḥ kāraṇairjanyamānatvadityasya ca ghaṭādāvapi bhāvādanaikāntikatvam;
buddhitvaviśeṣaṇapakṣe ca smṛtijñānenānaikāntikatvam । naitadevam; ayathārthabhāvā-
bhāvo'tra pratijñātārthaḥ; na ca kaścid doṣaḥ ।।

“kathaṃ punarasāvanarthaḥ?” ityasya uttarabhāṣyam “hiṃsā hi sā, sā ca
pratiṣiddhā” iti । etadvikalpya dūṣayitumāha—codanālakṣaṇamityardhena । yadi
tāvatkaraṇabhūtāḥ śyenādayo'tra hiṃsāśabdenābhidhīyante, tadopakramopasaṃhārayorvirodhaḥ;
